folder: Grand Street & Mott Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Grand Street, north side, west from but not including Mott Street.

August 28, 1930.

P. L. Sperr.

(1)
A vendors stand of girls apparel at Mott Street, near the S.W. corner of Grand Street.
August 28, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.

(2)
Another, of womens apparel in front of a stable door at 139 Mott Street.
August 28, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.

(3)
Another at 114th Street and First Ave.
August 18, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
